Music Explorer

A simple web app to search songs and artists using the Deezer API. Users can search for tracks, view album covers, and play 30-second previews directly in the browser.

Project Spec

Goal: Let users discover music by searching songs or artists and listening to previews.

Features:


Search bar to look up any song or artist
Display results as cards (cover, title, artist)
30-second audio preview player for each track


Tech stack:


HTML, CSS, JavaScript (vanilla)
Deezer API (via a CORS proxy for browser requests)


How to Run

Open index.html in your browser, or visit the deployed GitHub Pages link.

How it Works


Type a song or artist name in the search bar and press Enter or click Search.
The app fetches matching tracks from the Deezer API.
Results are displayed as cards with cover art, title, artist, and a preview player.


Deployment

Deployed using GitHub Pages.
